lines.text: A rabbit? Ha ha ha ha! A rabbit.
Yeah, Ha ha ha ha! A rabbit. And just who do you think you are?
Who am I? I'm Sam Von Schmamm the Hessian, that's who I am, and I've got you outnumbered one to one. Surrender or die, rabbit!
Now just a minute, Von Schmamm the Hessian. This happens to be me native soil and I like it. In fact, I love it.
And no Hessian oppression is gonna put me off'n it. So just try and take it.
I'm a Hessian without no aggression. If you can't beat 'em, join 'em.
You better say your prayers, you flea-bitten varmit! I'm a-gonna blow you to smithereenies!
Ah, your brother blows bubble gum!
